###################### REAL TIME FACE RECOGNITION BY OPENCV ####################

******************************* Methodology ************************************

I applied simple Machine Learning Algorithms on it. i scrap the encodings of known images and Train my model on it. it gives 89.67 % accuracy on testing data.




******************************** Resources *************************************
                             Ubuntu:18.04 / Env - Python3 

1. I use "face_recognition" python module. i give some Training Images to it. i use "SVM" algorithm for Training the array data.
-----you can easily install it by "sudo pip3 install face_recognition".


2. I handel the webcam by OpenCV and Process all Image Processing By it.
-----you can easily install it's main and contrib modules by "sudo pip3 install opencv-contrib-python".

****************************** Step By Step Guide ******************************

step 1. install the reqiurements.txt file.
		$ pip3 install -r requirements.txt

step 2. give the image's path and name in friendsreco.py file on line - 10.


step 3. Run the python code.
		$ python3 friendsreco.py


